## ததஅக

[ upatēcam ]  
  
உபதேசரத்தினமாலை upatēcarattiṉamālai  
பெ. id. a poetical treatise in tamilby maṇavāḷamamuṉikaḷ  
15th c. explainingthe vaiṣṇ. traditions and describing the livesand teachings of the long lineage of vaiṣṇ.ācāryas; மணவாளமாமுனிகளியற்றிய ஒரு வைணவசம்பிரதாய நூல்  
s. (உப) teaching. spiritual instruction  
doctrine  
போதகம்;  
2. advice  
புத்தி  
s. [pref. உப.]  
spirit ual instruction  
teaching  
போத கம்  
2. (fig.) advice in general  
3. the initiation of the pupil into the mysteries of his religion  
சமயாசாரவுபதேசம்  
4. a form of secret instruction  
incan tations  
c.  
given by the guru to his disciple  
on his admission into any of the four stages or degrees  
மந்திரோபதேசம். wils. p  
